E1:

Reat & React DOM

react library for core functionality
react dom library for handling DOM

-----------------

need a root element to render any element to the DOM

react.createElement(1,2,3);

got 3 arguments
1. type of html element tag - li div h1 h2 etc
2. object for providing attributes to html element like id, color - {id:"",color:""}
3. children for the html element - like text to show for a header tag. <h1>"Hello"</h1>

reactDOM.createRoot(set reference to any element like a div with id "root") - <div id="root"></div>

root.render(createdElement);

-----------------------------------